@startuml

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor<<context>>  #E8F4F8
    BackgroundColor<<state>>    #FFE8CC
    BorderColor #444444
}
hide empty members

title Door2 - Class Diagram (State Pattern)

interface DoorState {
    + {abstract} click(door : Door2) : void
    + {abstract} complete(door : Door2) : void
    + {abstract} status() : String
}

class Door2 <<context>> {
    - state : DoorState
    + click() : void
    + complete() : void
    + timeout() : void
    + setState(state : DoorState) : void
    + status() : String
}

class ClosedState   <<state>> implements DoorState
class OpeningState  <<state>> implements DoorState
class OpenState     <<state>> implements DoorState
class ClosingState  <<state>> implements DoorState
class StayOpenState <<state>> implements DoorState

Door2 "1" *-- "1" DoorState : state

note right of Door2
  <b>Context</b>
  현재 state 객체에 행위를 위임.
  click/complete 호출 시
  내부적으로 state.xxx(this) 실행.
  timeout은 예외적으로 Door2가 직접 관리.
end note

note right of DoorState
  <b>State 인터페이스</b>
  메소드에 Door2(this)를 받음.
  → ConcreteState가
     Context의 상태를 전이 가능
end note

note bottom of ClosedState
  <b>ConcreteStates</b>
  각자 자기 상태의 전이 규칙 캡슐화
  예: ClosedState.click(door)
      → door.setState(new OpeningState())
  ──
  <b>전이 책임의 분산</b>
  Door1의 거대한 if-else가
  5개 State 클래스로 분해됨
end note

@enduml
